Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.30,0:00:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在被星光照射的頂屋裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.90,0:00:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獨自一人聆聽著天空的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.55,0:00:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用玻璃的繃帶遮住眼睛行走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.20,0:00:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都是孤獨的馬戲團孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.85,0:00:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤身一人的悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.10,0:00:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,震動的繃帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.87,0:00:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撼動著心靈……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.35,0:01:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用溫柔的眼神期待與某人的相會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.05,0:01:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我耳邊細語「請留在我身邊」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.27,0:01:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Silent Voice
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.20,0:01:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們好不容易才回到宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.32,0:01:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是米查卻說要趕我們下新亞加瑪船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.48,0:01:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一氣就奪走新亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.23,0:01:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹的好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.84,0:01:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是..我們沒有外力支援\n能夠戰鬥下去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.49,0:01:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十八話 鐵壁,加姆羅菲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.30,0:02:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假隕石運入後就算搬完\n辛苦你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.45,0:02:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,代理艦長\n物資補給完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.29,0:02:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾美莉代理艦長?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.92,0:02:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有結果,沒結果...有結果!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.44,0:02:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布拉度艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.58,0:02:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是你要的資料\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.67,0:02:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有,這上面是我的留言\n你一定要走嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.95,0:02:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想讓新亞加瑪,繼續獲得補給物資\n我不出面不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.66,0:02:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是亞加瑪沒有艦長你便會...\n所以我才要請你去阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.59,0:02:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搬運作業完畢了\n艦長,請快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.24,0:02:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洗達跟冠武呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.33,0:03:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上船了,他們還拿著\n第三號殖民地的戰鬥分佈圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.50,0:03:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我走了,艾美莉\n艦長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.31,0:03:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,代理艦長,我們必須去追新亞加瑪\n就只有你跟我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.50,0:03:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那當然了,布然道格拉那達就沒有意義了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.26,0:03:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,代理艦長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.98,0:03:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了,我去就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.19,0:03:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,E攝影機輸入影像\nG攝影機開始輸入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.79,0:03:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊萊,你那邊怎樣?\n我正在忙著阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.28,0:03:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這...這樣...\n笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.58,0:03:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長應該是默默坐著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.90,0:03:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是..\n讓他搞吧讓他搞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.16,0:03:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,輸入完畢\n辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.89,0:03:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特雷斯,擴大G攝影機\n好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.42,0:03:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對照資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.32,0:04:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是第三號殖民地的殖民地群
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.37,0:04:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有這個?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.21,0:04:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度...\n都沒有敵人阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.95,0:04:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們到第三號殖民地去吧\n不行,敵人一定埋伏在某各地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.98,0:04:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有,我們不知道新吉翁軍\n再第三號殖民地的佈署
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.43,0:04:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是說要一直等下去\n會有人傳情報過來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.14,0:04:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的\n布拉度艦長會想辦法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.53,0:04:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特雷斯,繼續監視
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.74,0:04:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,你怎麼不先問一下艦長的意見!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.89,0:04:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是在節省時間\n你說什麼?  要打架嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.31,0:04:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別鬧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.59,0:04:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這時候打架的話\n會被莉娜罵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.84,0:04:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉...莉娜?\n我得趕快結束戰爭去接莉娜回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.43,0:04:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊萊,繼續索敵\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.48,0:04:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看讓捷度休息一下比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.36,0:04:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度只是太累了\n如果是這樣就還好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.10,0:04:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查,繼續索敵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.48,0:05:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了,左舷的攝影機\n被垃圾擋到了,再伸長出去   瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.72,0:05:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在,不在,在,不在,在...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.22,0:05:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,航道的計算交給電腦吧\n代理艦長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.63,0:05:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請別用這東西占卜航道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.84,0:05:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以為他們\n會待在原地不動嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.04,0:05:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特雷斯和凱撒他們還在亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.98,0:05:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是布拉度艦長不在阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.56,0:05:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布拉度艦長認為\n他們一定在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.24,0:05:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對的,對的\n那麼進入暗礁空域就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.70,0:05:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.33,0:05:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還不嫁人,如果有個萬一...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.91,0:05:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.72,0:05:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幫我準備信號彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.46,0:06:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,AMA-01X\nJAMRU FIN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.63,0:06:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照這情況\n會比預定要早10分中抵達安多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.75,0:06:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加姆羅菲的速度比預計的要快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.82,0:06:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有新型的MS和我們\n要打敗亞加瑪一點也不難阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.91,0:06:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以快速陞官了\n還能美女包圍呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.61,0:06:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進入暗礁空域,抵達安多拉2號,先試試身手吧\n瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.00,0:06:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,射的好德魯,隆恩\n戴尼,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.47,0:06:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那光線...是亞加瑪嗎!\n去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.29,0:06:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這樣發射信號彈\n被敵人發現的話怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.38,0:06:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人至少比新亞加瑪遙遠\n可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.43,0:07:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要亞加瑪在這空域\n自然就能聯絡上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.05,0:07:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,代理艦長,左舷有飛行部隊接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.74,0:07:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.83,0:07:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與資料不符\n什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.43,0:07:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,代理艦長,快準備戰鬥\n對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.23,0:07:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米加戰車還沒準備好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.21,0:07:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裏發射信號彈絕不尋常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.32,0:07:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是遇上敵人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.57,0:07:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.06,0:07:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好玩了,發射這麼多假隕石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.33,0:07:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,展示我們的力量給他們看吧\n好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.88,0:07:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人接近速度沒有減慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.27,0:07:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們都放這麼多假隕石了...\n快發射彈藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.98,0:07:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,假隕石太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.69,0:07:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沉沒吧,船塢艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.00,0:08:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布拉度艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.69,0:08:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快到信號彈的發射點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.54,0:08:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是敵人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.65,0:08:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿...在那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.43,0:08:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然沒錯,艾美莉真是的...\n這下子可能來不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.85,0:08:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉\n什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.09,0:08:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,往我所說的方向發炮吧\n從這裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.04,0:08:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想看到拉比安羅茲燃燒阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.63,0:08:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.59,0:08:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這個射線軸,發射!\n後果我可不管阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.90,0:08:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打中了\n還不知道打中什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.06,0:08:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可是捷度阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.62,0:09:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戴尼,沒事吧?\n推進器被打中了,撤退吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.51,0:09:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是都戰鬥到這個地步了...\n我們的敵人是亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.94,0:09:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在還趕的上\n與馬士文大人的約定時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.34,0:09:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.44,0:09:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要管小嘍囉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.80,0:09:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要打倒亞加瑪\n陞官才會快的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.93,0:09:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了!逃走了\n代理艦長,我們得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.43,0:09:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連Z高達的資料中\n都找不到的敵人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.93,0:09:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是新型MS\n往第三殖民地走了,這表示...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.65,0:09:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們跟舊吉翁的技術人員會合了\n好像很難對付...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.20,0:09:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聚集各位是為了轉交\n布拉度艦長的親筆信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.62,0:10:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,信當然是由我這位艦長接收了\n我看看,我要讀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.78,0:10:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新吉翁進入第三號殖民地\n對奧干而言是危險的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.82,0:10:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我命令你們打倒新吉翁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.23,0:10:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位是新人類,一定可以完成任務的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.25,0:10:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有,不實行命令時\n你們將被視為叛徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.78,0:10:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並會受到奧干與地球聯邦的追討
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.81,0:10:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?這根本是恐嚇信阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.59,0:10:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不是軍人\n對阿,捷度   沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.04,0:10:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正我本來就打算去第三號殖民地\n我們會有薪水的吧,艾美莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.94,0:10:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這當然...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.17,0:10:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那麼想要錢嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.86,0:10:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰爭結束後是需要錢的阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.09,0:10:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想送莉娜去讀好的學校\n捷度,你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.72,0:11:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查!說的對,想讓莉娜幸福\n當然是需要錢的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.27,0:11:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就接下這交易吧\n對,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.11,0:11:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有布拉度艦長的留言要播了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.66,0:11:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位,你們已經能獨當一面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.83,0:11:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己判斷,自己作戰\n自己堅持自己的主張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.37,0:11:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我不在多說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.86,0:11:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,比查,伊萊,莫迪\n艾莉,露卡,奇斯,特雷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.32,0:11:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布拉度艦長...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.59,0:11:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,加油吧!  嗯  好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.68,0:11:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等阿,捷度...\n別多說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.84,0:11:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了\n我們向第三殖民地出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.87,0:11:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,脫離暗礁空域的時候\n可能會受到敵人攻擊,知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.17,0:11:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不..\n捷度瘋了,絕對瘋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.42,0:12:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是來保護第三殖民地的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.91,0:12:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是來當你部下的,你最好記住這點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.18,0:12:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沙多隊長!\n算了吧,伊莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.98,0:12:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是,馬士文大人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.41,0:12:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連第三號殖民地的舊人員\n也收服不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.87,0:12:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更不可能打倒新亞加瑪的阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.20,0:12:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新的戰艦沒什麼了不起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.76,0:12:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戴尼,德魯,隆恩,現在抵達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.49,0:12:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們來了\n加姆羅菲三劍客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.66,0:12:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加姆羅菲可不是臨時湊成的三人組阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.72,0:12:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.03,0:13:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上請你們加入任務\n請去休息待命吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.34,0:13:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.43,0:13:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在暗礁空域曾與敵人的船塢艦接觸\n亞加瑪應該在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.06,0:13:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了不起,確實厲害\n又是一批難以控制的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.04,0:13:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們是專家,瞭解自己的立場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.40,0:13:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問題是裏亞斯隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.38,0:13:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依莉亞,我有個計策\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.65,0:13:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好聽著,裏亞斯隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.99,0:13:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們才是將新吉翁軍的傳統\n傳續給新吉翁的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.14,0:13:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別讓馬士文得意啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.56,0:13:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,推進器還在維修,再等一會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.81,0:13:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.14,0:13:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裏亞斯隊先走了\n這個距離不需要推進器也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.55,0:13:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加姆羅菲1號,戴尼\n加姆羅菲2號,隆恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.73,0:14:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加姆羅菲3號,德魯\n加姆羅菲出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.62,0:14:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人在附近\n大家都很拚命阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.74,0:14:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快脫離暗礁空域了\n比查也去準備MS吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.15,0:14:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長必須留在這裏,不是嗎?\n是,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.02,0:14:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,E攝影機的影像...\n快核對資料   瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.62,0:14:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新亞加瑪來電,發現敵人的MS,總共有十架\n好像已經發現了我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.90,0:14:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼多嗎?我們的MS那麼少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.25,0:14:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請冷靜下來\n先放假隕石再加炮擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.88,0:14:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,準備對空炮火\n放出假隕石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.53,0:15:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查,你要出擊阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.40,0:15:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是艦長\n百式給伊萊駕駛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.35,0:15:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊萊必須操作機器的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.91,0:15:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZZ高達,出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.82,0:15:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米加戰車,出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.85,0:15:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達,出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.93,0:15:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?後方有攻擊??
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.26,0:15:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後方有敵人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.44,0:15:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是拉比安羅茲在開炮阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.52,0:15:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們正在出擊中\快停止炮擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.45,0:15:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停止炮擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.47,0:15:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那光芒很近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.36,0:15:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裏亞斯隊,散開來包圍敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.96,0:15:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必說我也知道\n我知道敵人的份量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.77,0:15:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包在我身上就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.94,0:15:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沙多隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.44,0:15:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻擊!快攻擊\n廢話,你也來幫忙阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.75,0:15:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉比安羅茲在幹什麼的?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.19,0:15:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被穿過去了,敵人太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.45,0:16:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫迪,可以嗎?\n包在我身上,莫迪駕駛Mk2出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.11,0:16:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣阿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.79,0:16:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.50,0:16:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衝進心臟地帶的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.65,0:16:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快攻擊新亞加瑪艦橋的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.32,0:16:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是炮門的死角阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.26,0:16:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...不行了\n受死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.33,0:16:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?\n好像不是捷度他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.26,0:16:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是沙多隊長不對阿\n不聽我的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.92,0:16:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裏亞斯隊聽著\n隊長被亞加瑪打死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.81,0:16:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快擊沉亞加瑪\n這是替你們隊長報的仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.21,0:17:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長死了\n隊長..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.16,0:17:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.72,0:17:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看到剛才...\n別說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.44,0:17:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪沒被擊落對我們是好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.35,0:17:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戴尼,隆恩,ZZ高達來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.95,0:17:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擊落它,我們名氣會更高\n去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.83,0:17:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是新型的機體嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.80,0:17:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.67,0:17:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒底共有多少架阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.27,0:17:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被包圍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.56,0:17:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的三位一體攻擊\n是任何人都躲不過的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.64,0:18:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉,露卡!捷度陷入苦戰\n去支援他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.45,0:18:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也很忙阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.33,0:18:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查怎麼了?不是有百式嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.21,0:18:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你擔心捷度的話\n便出動支援他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.01,0:18:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是...我的立場...\n現在不是說那個的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.27,0:18:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人接近右舷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.62,0:18:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這時候還起內哄\n如果布柆度艦長在的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.12,0:18:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還在說什麼話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.03,0:18:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,現在就被擊敗的話\n等於是背叛了布拉度艦長阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.61,0:18:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開跟亞加瑪的通訊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.45,0:18:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查,快去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.91,0:18:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准命令艦長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.99,0:18:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快去吧,比查!那邊的艦橋由我掌管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.48,0:18:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是亞加瑪的艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.60,0:18:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長的工作是保護自己的戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.06,0:18:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不率先保護戰艦\n沒有人會承認你是艦長的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.16,0:18:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必你說我也知道\n我只是想看清戰局吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.18,0:18:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不在時要好好工作\n瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.20,0:18:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾美莉艦長好有威嚴阿\n跟布拉度艦長一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.58,0:19:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對阿,我們一心同體了\n前方炮火不夠密集阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.16,0:19:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她這麼容易激動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.16,0:19:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?敵人開始團結了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.26,0:19:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相較之下我們...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.26,0:19:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們休想在逞威風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.81,0:19:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不歸是ZZ高達,確實名不虛傳\n真值得我們誇獎 可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.51,0:19:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.22,0:19:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,你太放水了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.37,0:19:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些新型機一個人很難處理的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.98,0:19:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是不是變呆了?\n我很正常阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.15,0:19:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管他一架還是兩架...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.62,0:19:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什...什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.90,0:19:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我說麻煩阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.56,0:19:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幹什麼,捷度\n我問你才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.27,0:20:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些傢伙我可以獨自處理的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.25,0:20:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以一個人對抗阿\n什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.72,0:20:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥你知道嗎,冷靜下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.88,0:20:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了,莉娜,可是比查那傢伙...過來\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.18,0:20:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查,你聽著\n我會預料敵人的動作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.78,0:20:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你辦的到嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.56,0:20:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辦不到就死定了\n怎麼這樣?...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.70,0:20:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打算兩個一起死嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.54,0:20:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別小看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.06,0:20:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查!\n是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.79,0:20:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德魯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.41,0:20:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是湊巧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.06,0:20:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那邊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.73,0:20:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能的..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.71,0:20:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到隊長之死\n會令裏亞斯隊士氣大減的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.40,0:20:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來聰明的作法是下次再來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.17,0:21:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撤退命令?\n德魯,隆恩,撤退  可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.05,0:21:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別逞強了\n人死了就什麼都沒有了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.08,0:21:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好了,剛才的MS...\n不,是MA,很可怕阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.45,0:21:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是,但我好像聽到莉娜的聲音?\n那是什麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.58,0:21:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查你也聽到嗎?是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.90,0:21:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.99,0:21:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是這樣,我感覺到莉娜了\n那不是幽靈或鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.21,0:21:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.96,0:22:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我親眼看到的沙多隊長\n被亞加瑪的炮火所打中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.76,0:22:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真正可恨的是亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.63,0:22:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次我們一定替隊長報仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.01,0:22:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的對\n戰場什麼事都有可能發生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.94,0:22:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著,在我指揮下打倒亞加瑪\n你們便可以快速陞官了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.20,0:22:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待遇絕對比過去好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.42,0:22:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我是\n哈曼大人親信的騎士阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.30,0:22:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成百 成萬 上億的繁星啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.49,0:22:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何只是閃耀而已 展示你言語的能力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.55,0:23:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我也能不回頭地 讓心靈出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.70,0:23:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若能把多如繁星的生命儲存的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.65,0:23:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把整個銀河也化作光芒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.35,0:23:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,化作緊握在掌心的 生命的重量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.32,0:23:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我仍未能看見宇宙的路標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.22,0:23:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手掌觸摸著一千萬年的光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.32,0:23:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們本應該接近SIDE 3\n卻接受了民間的貨物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.92,0:23:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還救了載著月月的人們的船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.70,0:23:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為太忙了 忽略了藏在貨物裏的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.37,0:24:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 蒙德做得好！\n就是要靠力量！拉莎拉也這樣說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.55,0:24:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必須得加油 對吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.07,0:24:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下集 高達ZZ 再遇莎拉莎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.49,0:24:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不斷出現的偶然真可怕！

